*Drugim* rukama je sklopio čvrst zagrljaj. (He embraced her tightly with his other hands.)

*Drugim* rečima, nisu bili srećni. (In other words, they weren't happy.)

Od *drugim* ljudi naučio je da se trudi. (He learned from other people to strive.)

Njegova *druga* polovina je tu sa njim. (His other half is here with him.)

Ona je lupila *drugim* osobama. (She was hitting other people.)

*Drugim* delom, on je bio veoma uspešan. (In other parts, he was very successful.)